      <title>纽蒙特在重大公司重组中削减管理职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/newmont-cuts-management-jobs-in-major-corporate-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，作为全面公司改革的一部分，纽蒙特公司解雇了近十几名管理人员，其中包括一名执行团队成员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/newmont-cuts-management-jobs-in-major-corporate-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:25:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利大亨卡尔塔吉罗内增持资产管理公司 Anima 的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/italian-tycoon-caltagirone-raises-stake-in-asset-manager-anima</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利建筑业大亨弗朗西斯科·加埃塔诺·卡尔塔吉罗内 (Francesco Gaetano Caltagirone) 增持了 Anima Holding 的股份，以便在席卷该国金融服务业的交易浪潮中获得更多影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/italian-tycoon-caltagirone-raises-stake-in-asset-manager-anima</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新泽西州交通局首席执行官任职七年后将辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nj-transit-ceo-to-resign-after-seven-years-running-the-agency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州交通局首席执行官兼总裁凯文·科贝特 (Kevin Corbett) 将于下个月卸任，他已执掌全美最大的公共交通提供商之一近七年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nj-transit-ceo-to-resign-after-seven-years-running-the-agency</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳前总统获得巨大授权解决通货膨胀问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ghana-election-mahama-faces-slew-of-challenges-after-biggest-mandate-in-decades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳选举前总统约翰·马哈马重返他八年前担任的职务，赋予他强有力的授权来解决这个西非国家沉重的债务负担和高昂的生活成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/ghana-election-mahama-faces-slew-of-challenges-after-biggest-mandate-in-decades</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:03:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国暗示2025年将出台更多刺激措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/china-signals-more-stimulus-is-coming-in-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国暗示准备在 2025 年推出更多刺激措施。此举被视为对即将爆发的中美贸易战、中国经济低迷以及即将上任的唐纳德·特朗普政府的回应。彭博社的刘约翰报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-12-09/china-signals-more-stimulus-is-coming-in-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:52:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷石油产量有望取代哥伦比亚，成为南美三大石油产国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/argentine-oil-output-is-poised-to-oust-colombia-from-south-america-s-top-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷的页岩钻探热潮使该国即将超越其地区竞争对手哥伦比亚，成为南美洲三大原油生产国之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/argentine-oil-output-is-poised-to-oust-colombia-from-south-america-s-top-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院裁决为卢拉财政计划制造新障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/top-court-ruling-creates-new-hurdle-for-lula-s-fiscal-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西最高法院的一名法官拒绝了重新考虑一项裁决的请求，该裁决使得司法部门、政府和国会之间的关系变得复杂，并可能削弱总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦争取财政紧缩计划批准的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/top-court-ruling-creates-new-hurdle-for-lula-s-fiscal-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亿滋国际考虑收购美国巧克力制造商好时</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/mondelez-said-to-explore-takeover-of-us-chocolate-maker-hershey</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，零食和糖果公司亿滋国际 (Mondelez International Inc.) 正在探索收购美国标志性巧克力制造商好时公司 (Hershey Co.)，这笔交易可能打造出一家总销售额近 500 亿美元的食品巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/mondelez-said-to-explore-takeover-of-us-chocolate-maker-hershey</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:05:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新日铁为赢得美国工人支持做最后努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司公布了其在美国钢铁公司旗下美国钢厂的支出计划，这是其为争取工人和政界人士支持收购这家匹兹堡钢铁制造商而做出的最后一项努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/nippon-steel-clarifies-spending-pledge-in-effort-to-save-us-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 13:03:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街强劲反弹在 CPI 上涨中受挫：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市在强劲上涨之后回落，市场有望创下 2019 年以来的最佳年度表现，交易员正在等待有助于影响美联储利率前景的关键通胀数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/asian-markets-cautious-amid-geopolitical-tensions-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 22:41:08 GMT</pubDate>
